\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 About this compilation\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sb120\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf0 This is a compilation of the 
\f2\i Acts Interpretation Act 1901
\f1\i0  that shows the text of the law as amended and in force on 11\'a0December 2024 (the 
\f3\i\b compilation date
\f1\i0\b0 ).\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The notes at the end of this compilation (the 
\f3\i\b endnotes
\f1\i0\b0 ) include information about amending laws and the amendment history of provisions of the compiled law.\
\pard\tx5640\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sb120\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Uncommenced amendments\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 The effect of uncommenced amendments is not shown in the text of the compiled law. Any uncommenced amendments affecting the law are accessible on the Register (www.legislation.gov.au). The details of amendments made up to, but not commenced at, the compilation date are underlined in the endnotes. For more information on any uncommenced amendments, see the Register for the compiled law.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sb120\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Application, saving and transitional provisions for provisions and amendments\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0

