\f0\b \cf0 Editorial changes\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 For more information about any editorial changes made in this compilation, see the endnotes.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Presentational changes\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 The 
\f2\i Legislation Act 2003
\f1\i0  provides for First Parliamentary Counsel to make presentational changes to a compilation. Presentational changes are applied to give a more consistent look and feel to legislation published on the Register, and enable the user to more easily navigate those documents.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sb120\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Modifications\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1933\sl260\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 If the compiled law is modified by another law, the compiled law operates as modified but the modification does not amend the text of the law. Accordingly, this compilation does not show the text of the compiled law as modified. For more information on any modifications, see the Register for the compiled law.\
