\f3\i\b Administrative Arrangements Order
\f1\i0\b0 :\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	means an instrument (a 
\f3\i\b primary AAO
\f1\i0\b0 ) made by the Governor\uc0\u8209 General that is described as an Administrative Arrangements Order; and\
	(b)	includes an instrument made by the Governor\uc0\u8209 General that:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	amends a primary AAO; or\
	(ii)	revokes a primary AAO and substitutes a new primary AAO.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1985\fi-851\ri1933\sb122\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf0 Note:	The Administrative Arrangements Order sets out, from time to time, the matters dealt with by Departments of State of the Commonwealth together with the legislation administered by the Ministers for those Departments.\
