\fs18 \cf0 Note:	Substituted reference orders under section\'a019B may have effect in relation to days before the orders are made.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\fs22 \cf0 	(3)	To avoid doubt, if, because of this section, a provision of an Act is taken to require anything to be done by or in relation to any one of 2 or more Ministers, the provision is not taken to require it to be done in any particular case by or in relation to more than one of those Ministers.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

