\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 38  Reference to Acts\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf0 	(1)	An Act passed by the Parliament of the Commonwealth may be referred to by the word \'93Act\'94 alone.\
	(2)	An Act passed by the Parliament of the United Kingdom may be referred to by the term \'93Imperial Act\'94.\
	(3)	An Act passed by the Parliament of a State may be referred to by the term \'93State Act\'94.\
	(4)	An Act passed by the legislature of a Territory may be referred to by the term \'93Territory Act\'94.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 39  Numbering of Acts\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf0 		The Acts passed in each secular year shall be numbered in regular arithmetical series, beginning with the number 1, in the order in which the Governor\uc0\u8209 General assents thereto, or makes known the Sovereign\'92s assent thereto.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 40  Citation of Acts and instruments\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i\b0\fs22 \cf0 Citation of Acts, legislative instruments and notifiable instruments\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf0 	(1A)	In any Act, instrument or document:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	an Act may be cited by:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	the short title of the Act; or\
	(ii)	the secular year in which it was passed, and its number; or\
	(iii)	a unique identifier given to the Act in accordance with rules prescribed under the 
\f2\i Legislation Act 2003
\f1\i0 ; and\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(b)	a legislative instrument or notifiable instrument may be cited by:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	any name the instrument gives itself; or\
	(ii)	a unique identifier given to the instrument in accordance with rules prescribed under the 
\f2\i Legislation Act 2003
\f1\i0 ; or\
	(iii)	if the instrument was numbered under a Commonwealth law\'97the year it was made and its number, together with a reference (if necessary) to the kind of instrument; or\
	(iv)	if the instrument was notified or published in the Gazette\'97the date and (if necessary) number and page of the Gazette in which it was notified or published; or\
	(v)	the date it was made, together with a reference to the Act or instrument, and (if necessary) provision, under which it was made.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf0 Citation of Imperial Acts, State Acts and Territory Acts\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf0 	(1)	In any Act, instrument, or document:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(b)	any Imperial Act may be cited by its short title (if any) or in such other manner as is sufficient in an Imperial Act; and\
	(c)	any State Act may be cited by a reference to the State by the Parliament whereof the Act was passed, together with such mode of reference as is sufficient in Acts passed by such Parliament; and\
	(d)	any Territory Act may be cited by a reference to the Territory by whose legislature the Act was passed, together with such mode of reference as is sufficient in Acts passed by that legislature.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(2)	Any enactment may be cited by reference to the part, section, subsection, or other division of the Act, Imperial Act, State Act or Territory Act, in which the enactment is contained.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 40A  References to the new corporations and ASIC legislation\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf0 	(1)	A reference in an Act to:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	an Act, or regulations or another instrument, that is part of the new corporations legislation or the new ASIC legislation; or\
	(b)	a provision, or group of provisions, of such an Act, regulations or other instrument;\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 is taken to include a reference to:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(c)	the corresponding part, provision or provisions of the old corporations legislation or the old ASIC legislation; and\
	(d)	any relevant earlier law.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(2)	Subsection\'a0(1) does not apply to:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	a reference in an Act that is part of the new corporations legislation or the new ASIC legislation; or\
	(b)	a reference in the 
\f2\i Corporations (Repeals, Consequentials and Transitionals) Act 2001
\f1\i0 ; or\
	(c)	a reference that identifies an Act that is part of the new corporations legislation or the new ASIC legislation as an Act to be amended; or\
	(d)	a reference in a provision that applies an Act that is part of the new corporations legislation or the new ASIC legislation, or a provision or group of provisions, of such an Act to a particular matter (whether with or without modification).\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(3)	Subsection\'a0(1) has effect:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	subject to an express provision to the contrary in the Act concerned; and\
	(b)	subject to regulations made for the purposes of subsection\'a0(5).\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(4)	For the purposes of this section:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	the question whether a part, provision or provisions of the old corporations legislation 
\f3\i\b corresponds
\f1\i0\b0  to a part, provision or provisions of the new corporations legislation is to be determined in the same way as it is determined for the purposes of Part\'a010.1
\f2\i  
\f1\i0 of the 
\f2\i Corporations Act 2001
\f1\i0 ; and\
	(b)	the question whether a part, provision or provisions of the old ASIC legislation 
\f3\i\b corresponds
\f1\i0\b0  to a part, provision or provisions of the new ASIC legislation is to be determined in the same way as it is determined for the purposes of Part\'a016 of the 
\f2\i Australian Securities and Investments Commission Act 2001
\f1\i0 .\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(5)	The regulations may provide that subsection\'a0(1) does not apply in relation to a particular reference, or class of references, in an Act.\
	(6)	In this section:\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f3\i\b \cf0 new ASIC legislation
\f1\i0\b0  has the same meanings as in Part\'a016 of the 
\f2\i Australian Securities and Investments Commission Act 2001
\f1\i0 .\

\f3\i\b new corporations legislation
\f1\i0\b0  has the same meanings as in Part\'a010.1
\f2\i  
\f1\i0 of the 
\f2\i Corporations Act 2001
\f1\i0 .\

\f3\i\b old ASIC legislation
\f1\i0\b0  has the same meanings as in Part\'a016 of the 
\f2\i Australian Securities and Investments Commission Act 2001
\f1\i0 .\

\f3\i\b old corporations legislation
\f1\i0\b0  has the same meanings as in Part\'a010.1
\f2\i  
\f1\i0 of the 
\f2\i Corporations Act 2001
\f1\i0 .\

\f3\i\b relevant earlier law
\f1\i0\b0 , in relation to a provision of the old corporations legislation, or the old ASIC legislation, means a law that was:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	a corresponding previous law (as defined for the purposes of that provision or provisions that included that provision); or\
	(b)	a relevant previous law (as defined for the purposes of that provision or provisions that included that provision).\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb280\partightenfactor0

